sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant View as MyDevicePage
    participant Dialog as ReturnDialog
    participant VM as ViewModel
    participant UC as ReturnDeviceUseCase
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>View: Chọn 3 dòng thiết bị bằng CheckBox
    Note over View: Nút Return Selected được bật
    User->>View: Click Return Selected
    View->>Dialog: Hiển thị ContentDialog
    Note over Dialog: Bạn sắp trả 3 thiết bị<br/>Danh sách Model + IMEI<br/>Confirm / Cancel
    User->>Dialog: Click Confirm
    Dialog->>VM: ReturnCommand(selectedDeviceIds)
    VM->>UC: ExecuteAsync(deviceIds)
    UC->>DB: BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction
    Note over DB: UPDATE Available, Reserved<br/>DELETE BorrowedDevices WHERE Id IN
    DB-->>UC: Success
    UC-->>VM: Result
    VM->>VM: SyncService.Broadcast
    VM->>VM: Reload + xóa selection
